metadata.name: Remember your color of sky
metadata.description:
There are times you disappoint yourself

There are times you compare yourself to someone else and feel envious.

There are times you are made fun of and hide your heart deep inside.

But, Please remember

You have your own "color".

There are "colors itâ€™s" that only you can use.

You don't have to be someone else.

You just have to be yourself.
